{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4c3629e503","title":"攻击丑化党员的右派言论（二）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"314ccc2630","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"4c3629e503"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1c35dc027c","name":"李寿国"},{"id":"2499a730cb","name":"云南大学"},{"id":"33b28108a4","name":"王孔渊"},{"id":"393686fd5a","name":"张熙"},{"id":"7e17ab93c1","name":"贺斌"},{"id":"98681f334c","name":"秦鸿谋"},{"id":"a801366d30","name":"谭东北"},{"id":"bf13ed07d6","name":"张铁波"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d7aeb4af34","type":"title","text":"攻击丑化党员的右派言论（二）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"ae679db92d","type":"authors","text":"云南大学秦鸿谋王孔渊李寿国贺斌张铁波谭东北张熙","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"3240a1c628","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员特权思想严重，发展到了专横的地步，党员‘只许州官放火，不许百姓点灯’，党员是顺我者生，逆我者死；党员碰不得，碰了就倒霉；党员都是靠抱着金字招牌吃饭的人。党内宗派主义严重，不见他们互相有斗争。党员飞扬拔扈，已经是既不可敬，又不可爱了。如果取消党员的称号，他们与群众没有区别。”（秦鸿谋）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"8d1a80bde6","type":"paragraph","text":"“革命是为了消灭阶级，为什么现在划分党、团员、群的阶级？在朝鲜是党团员冲锋在前，现在有些党员是在受享上冲锋。”（王孔渊）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"cccf9d05c7","type":"paragraph","text":"政治经济学教科书内云：带来剩余价值的货币谓之资本，根据这点，我主为一个人入党后就可以叫党员资本了，因为党员这一块金牌子可以获得许多剩余价值：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"5cafaa3feb","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）有牌子就有一切——名誉、地位、待遇。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"ac9bfe0e3c","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）有牌子可以进行各种冒名顶替的活动成为各种代表。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"469b0d0e4c","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）可以用牌子去感动利诱女朋友。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"1bd2ac57d5","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）可以随便干涉别人生活。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"0206f3cec7","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）可以迎接外宴。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"db87e1c894","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）总之，宪法上规定的人民所享受的一切权利，是指有金牌子的人而言的。惨哉！痛哉！群众的地位何在！”（李寿国）","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"fe5c5d7983","type":"paragraph","text":"“团支部是森罗殿，党支部是活阎王。党的档案制有如国民党的特务制度，组织上可以随便给你鉴定几条。”（贺斌）","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"305858e186","type":"paragraph","text":"“墙和沟是党员造成的，积极分子是筑墙控沟的义勇队。”（张铁波）","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"4b5d59a2f4","type":"paragraph","text":"“青年团与过去的‘三青团’没有区别，开黑名单……”（谭东北）","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"154178561d","type":"paragraph","text":"“有不少的党员，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"11d69826f2","type":"paragraph","text":"把自己的金字招牌，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"a83ba63473","type":"paragraph","text":"当着‘天方夜谭’上的‘神灯’，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"031163c933","type":"paragraph","text":"想一辈子受用不尽。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"562a5bf8ec","type":"paragraph","text":"这金字招牌的用法是这样：","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"00e0aa4cb3","type":"paragraph","text":"如果你需要点甚么，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"d737fca775","type":"paragraph","text":"你就把它敲出当当的响声，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"bec4cf5435","type":"paragraph","text":"你面前马上出现了你的仆人。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"9b13d753f1","type":"paragraph","text":"“你要甚么？我的主人，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"6a0798b936","type":"paragraph","text":"是小卧车？还是洋房？","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"a630715d07","type":"paragraph","text":"是要天上的那个月亮，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"f055590d7a","type":"paragraph","text":"还是要月宫中的那个姑娘！","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"b2dbe6d411","type":"paragraph","text":"一切你都用不着悲伤，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"9246a019a9","type":"paragraph","text":"一切都象你想的那样。”","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"59c04ddb3a","type":"paragraph","text":"“但是呵，我的主人！","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"5d98a7cae7","type":"paragraph","text":"你要小心，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"0cf61dd8f5","type":"paragraph","text":"不要把金字招牌，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"56e51ee15c","type":"paragraph","text":"敲得过响过长。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"4e1164c72f","type":"paragraph","text":"如果敲得过火了，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"97e0f98da2","type":"paragraph","text":"它就会发生破响。”（张熙）","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"},{"id":"eccd872093","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503"}],"page":{"id":"094fc4227c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c3629e503","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}